addDenomination(bytes8,address).details: The AO adds denomination and the contract address associated with it

params.denominationAddress: The address of the denomination TAOCurrency
params.denominationName: The name of the denomination, i.e ao, kilo, mega, etc.

exchangeDenomination(uint256,bytes8,byte.details: exchange `amount` TAOCurrency from `fromDenominationName` denomination to TAOCurrency in `toDenominationName` denomination

params.amount: The amount of TAOCurrency to exchange

fromBase(uint256,bytes8).details: convert TAOCurrency from base denomination to `denominationName` denomination,	in this case it's similar to web3.fromWei() functionality

params.denominationName: bytes8 name of the target TAOCurrency denomination
params.integerAmount: uint256 of the base amount to be converted

fromBase(uint256,bytes8).return: uint256 of the converted integer amount in target denominationuint256 of the converted fraction amount in target denomination

getBaseDenomination().return: the denomination short namethe denomination addressthe denomination public namethe denomination symbolthe denomination num of decimalsthe denomination multiplier (power of ten)

getDenominationByIndex(uint256).return: the denomination short namethe denomination addressthe denomination public namethe denomination symbolthe denomination num of decimalsthe denomination multiplier (power of ten)

getDenominationByName(bytes8).details: Get denomination info based on name
getDenominationByName(bytes8).return: the denomination short namethe denomination addressthe denomination public namethe denomination symbolthe denomination num of decimalsthe denomination multiplier (power of ten)

getDenominationExchangeById(bytes32).details: Get DenominationExchange information given an exchange ID
getDenominationExchangeById(bytes32).return: The name ID that performed the exchangeThe from denomination addressThe to denomination addressThe from denomination symbolThe to denomination symbolThe amount exchanged

isDenominationExist(bytes8).details: Check if denomination exist given a name

setNameFactoryAddress(address).details: The AO set the NameFactory Address

setNameTAOPositionAddress(address).details: The AO set the NameTAOPosition Address

setWhitelist(address,bool).details: Whitelist `_account` address to transact on behalf of others

toBase(uint256,uint256,bytes8).details: convert TAOCurrency from `denominationName` denomination to base denomination,	in this case it's similar to web3.toWei() functionality	 * Example: 9.1 Kilo should be entered as 9 integerAmount and 100 fractionAmount 9.02 Kilo should be entered as 9 integerAmount and 20 fractionAmount 9.001 Kilo should be entered as 9 integerAmount and 1 fractionAmount

params.denominationName: bytes8 name of the TAOCurrency denomination
params.fractionAmount: uint256 of the frational amount to be converted
params.integerAmount: uint256 of the integer amount to be converted

toBase(uint256,uint256,bytes8).return: uint256 converted amount in base denomination from target denomination

toHighestDenomination(uint256).details: Return the highest possible denomination given a base amount
toHighestDenomination(uint256).return: the denomination short namethe denomination addressthe integer amount at the denomination levelthe fraction amount at the denomination levelthe denomination public namethe denomination symbolthe denomination num of decimalsthe denomination multiplier (power of ten)

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfer ownership of The AO to new address

params._theAO: The new address to be transferred

updateDenomination(bytes8,address).details: The AO updates denomination address or activates/deactivates the denomination

params.denominationAddress: The address of the denomination TAOCurrency
params.denominationName: The name of the denomination, i.e ao, kilo, mega, etc.
